name: Reincarnation (Transformation cycle)#2
description:
PHYSICAL PAINTING
 Size: 60 × 80
 Oil paint on canvas
 Artist: Roya vali[instagram:roya valli]

The mortal and perishing body, the soul that remains, is reincarnated in another body. Until it reaches immortality, the body that accompanies the mortal and corrupt yogurt is the soul of man that remains.
